Spices & Seasonings Mayacamas Hollandaise Gourmet Sauce Mix
items.details: All natural. Gluten free. No trans fat. Mayacamas products are produced under strict procedures to ensure that they remain gluten free and are routinely tested for the presence of gluten. Product of USA.
items.directions: Makes 1-1/2 cups (12 oz) sauce. 1. Whisk together 1-1/4 cups (310 ml) milk and sauce mix and dissolve completely. 2. Stirring constantly, bring to a boil over a medium-high heat. 3. Reduce heat and add 2 to 4 tbsp (approx. 30-60 g) of butter (For low fat version, use 1-1/4 cups low fat milk and no butter.). Chef's Note: Add a few drops each of worcester and tabasco sauce. A favorite over eggs benedict, asparagus, and other vegetables, or as a sauce for lemon chicken. Salt to taste.
items.ingredients: All Natural Ingredients: Rice Flour, Whey (Milk Product) (Dehydrated), Natural Lemon Flavor (Dehydrated), Salt, Dried Egg Yolk, Organic Sugar, Paprika, Citric Acid, Spices, Guar Gum.
